                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> <span>Flexible Learning: Access your courses 24/7. Learn at your own pace, whether you're balancing work, studies, or personal commitments.</span></li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/Home/ReadMore" class="read-more"><span>Read More</span><i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </section><!-- /About Section -->
